## Setup

```bash
python -m venv .venv
source .venv/bin/activate  # Windows: .venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -e ".[dev]"
```
{% if include_precommit %}

Install pre-commit hooks (runs ruff and other checks before each commit):

```bash
pre-commit install
```

Run all hooks manually:

```bash
pre-commit run --all-files
```
{% endif %}

## Usage

```bash
python -m app.main
```

## Development

```bash
# Run tests
pytest

# Lint and format
ruff check .
ruff format .
```
